<topic id='supporting_definition_information_standards_notice.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Supporting Information: Information Standards Notice - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
An 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_information_standards_notice">Information Standards Notice</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_information_standards_notice">ISN</xref>) is either a notice of an:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
Information Standard approved by the 
                                <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                        keyref="supporting_definition_information_standards_board_for_health_and_social_care">Information Standards Board for Health and Social Care</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                        keyref="supporting_definition_information_standards_board_for_health_and_social_care">ISB</xref>)                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                     keyref="supporting_definition_information_standard_and_collection__including_extraction_">Information Standard and Collection (including Extraction)</xref>
               <p>
 (<xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                        keyref="supporting_definition_information_standard_and_collection__including_extraction_">ISCE</xref>) accepted by the 
                                <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                        keyref="supporting_definition_standardisation_committee_for_care_information">Standardisation Committee for Care Information</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                        keyref="supporting_definition_standardisation_committee_for_care_information">SCCI</xref>) for formal approval by the 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_department_of_health_and_social_care">Department of Health and Social Care</xref>
 or 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
               </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                     keyref="supporting_definition_information_standard_and_collection__including_extraction_">Information Standard and Collection (including Extraction)</xref>
               <p>
 approved by the 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_data_coordination_board">Data Coordination Board</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_data_coordination_board">DCB</xref>).                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
An 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_information_standards_notice">Information Standards Notice</xref>
 was previously known as a 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_information_standards_notice">Data Set Change Notice</xref>
 (DSCN).        </p>
      <p>
When a health and social care 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>
 in England receives an 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_information_standards_notice">Information Standards Notice</xref>, they ensure that they and their contractors comply with the notice as specified.        </p>
      <p>
Further information on 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_information_standards_notice">Information Standards Notices</xref>, see the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 website at 
              <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/data-and-information/information-standards/information-standards-and-data-collections-including-extractions"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Information Standards and Collections (Including Extractions)</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
Details of all published 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_information_standards_notice">Information Standards Notices</xref>
 can be found at the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 website: at 
              <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/data-and-information/information-standards/information-standards-and-data-collections-including-extractions/publications-and-notifications"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Publication and Notification</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
